    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it looks just as stunning as it did on the showroom floor! It\u2019s been kept spotless, drives like a total dream, and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
