    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade example of the 996.2 Carrera 4S, featuring the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six mated to a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. This chassis retains its factory widebody dimensions and viscous-coupled AWD system with zero parasitic lash. The powerplant benefits from a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. Suspension kinematics remain factory-spec with original Bilstein damping units and unperished bushings. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors with zero lipping. Cosmetically, the paint depth is uniform across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or UV degradation on the dash. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
