    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features original, mirror-finish paint with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the interior is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple with no creasing on the bolsters, the carpets are pristine, and every switchgear retains its crisp, factory tactile feel. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with all fluids recently flushed and high-performance tires with near-full tread. There are no leaks, no rattles, and no deferred maintenance items. This is a rare, investment-grade example intended for the most discerning collector who demands perfection in every detail.",
      "price": 44500.0,
