      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear or mechanical compromise. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. This represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled integrity and aesthetic perfection. Inspections by appointment only.",
