      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one! Not a scratch, smells like new, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
